'''菲律宾民族民主阵线'''（{{lang-fil|Pambansang Demokratikong Prente ng Pilipinas}}，缩写为PDPP；{{lang-en|National Democratic Front of the Philippines}}，缩写为NDF或NDFP）成立于1973年4月24日，是[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]的一个群众基础广泛的[[左翼|左翼]]政治联盟（“革命统一战线组织”）。由进步团体、工会、农会、土著权益组织、左翼政党及其它相关组织组成。<ref name="about">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ndfp.org/about/|title=NATIONAL DEMOCRATIC FRONT OF THE PHILIPPINES|work=www.ndfp.org|access-date=2018-03-07|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180306142351/https://www.ndfp.org/about/|archive-date=2018-03-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 它的意识形态是[[反帝國主義|反帝国主义]]、[[共产主义|共产主义]]、[[社会主义|社会主义]]。它的代表人物有[[何塞·马利亚·西松|何塞·马利亚·西松]]和[[路易斯·贾兰多尼|路易斯·贾兰多尼]]。它曾派代表作为观察员参加[[国际共产主义研讨会|国际共产主义研讨会]]。该联盟的主导者是[[菲律宾共产党|菲律宾共产党]]。它是更广泛的菲律宾左翼政治联盟[[民族民主运动|民族民主运动]]的成员。<ref name=GMANewsMar14>{{cite news|last=VERSCHUUR-BALLO|first=CHARED|title=No vacuum in NPA leadership despite Tiamzon couple’s arrest –Joma|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/354576/news/nation/no-vacuum-in-npa-leadership-despite-tiamzon-couple-s-arrest-joma|accessdate=30 March 2014|newspaper=GMA News|date=March 28, 2014|archive-date=2016-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924050446/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/354576/news/nation/no-vacuum-in-npa-leadership-despite-tiamzon-couple-s-arrest-joma|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==目标==
菲律宾民族民主阵线提出了12项方案，以实现“民族解放和民主，力求为所有渴望真正的民族自由和民主、持久和平和进步菲律宾的国外和国内的社会阶层、部门、团体和个人提供统一的广泛基础。”<ref>{{cite web|title=12 Point Program of the NDFP|url=http://www.ndfp.net/joom15/index.php/about-the-ndfp-mainmenu-27/12-point-program-mainmenu-29.html|accessdate=12 October 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120802050142/http://www.ndfp.net/joom15/index.php/about-the-ndfp-mainmenu-27/12-point-program-mainmenu-29.html|archivedate=August 2, 2012|website=www.ndfp.net|quote=The NDFP's general program for national liberation and democracy seeks to provide a broad basis of unity for all social classes, sectors, groups and individual Filipinos here and abroad desirous of genuine national freedom and democracy, lasting peace and a progressive Philippines.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Twelve Points of the NDF Program|work=www.ndfp.org|url=https://www.ndfp.org/about/the-twelve-points-of-the-ndf-program/|accessdate=2018-03-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215170456/https://www.ndfp.org/about/the-twelve-points-of-the-ndf-program/|archivedate=2017-02-15}}</ref>

